RefactoringConfigHenshin

public RefactoringConfigHenshin(java.lang.String projectName,
                                java.lang.String refactoringId,
                                java.lang.String menuLabel,
                                java.lang.String namespaceURI,
                                java.lang.String createChangeFileName)
Constructor used for the new model refactoring to be generated.

Parameters:
projectName - Name of the project the model refactoring code has to be generated to.
refactoringId - Id of the model refactoring that has to be generated.
menuLabel - The label that shall appear before applying the model refactoring.
namespaceURI - Namespace of the models the model refactoring has to be generated for.
createChangeFileName - Name of the Henshin file used for executing the EMF model refactoring.
